w1038 &Cx1f; wstm-
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Japan-StockClosing     12-22 0042
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Japan-Stock Closing </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
