<HEADLINE>
Netanyahu ridicules rivals, demands Palestinian guarantees
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; AP Photos planned &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES in grafs 10-11 with Barak pledge to revive peace
process, Sharon anecdote, graf 17. TRIMS. &QL; 
 &UR; By RON KAMPEAS &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   JERUSALEM (AP) _ Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu opened what
promised to be a bare-knuckles re-election campaign Tuesday by
