	   LONDON _ China ordered a round-the-world balloon expedition to
land Tuesday, expedition organizers said, but they protested that
they didn't dare because of darkness, cloud cover and the rugged
terrain. BALLOON QUEST.
	   ROME _ A Rome prosecutor has asked that Abdullah Ocalan be put
back in jail, saying the Kurdish rebel leader must be kept under
surveillance in case an appeals court rules in favor of his
extradition to Turkey. ITALY-KURDISH REBEL.
