 &UR; By ELENA BECATOROS &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   SKOPJE, Macedonia (AP) _ In an indication of improved ties
between two Balkan neighbors, Greece's foreign minister arrived in
Macedonia on Tuesday for a series of meetings with government
officials.
	   Theodoros Pangalos' one-day trip is the first official visit by
