Amsterdam police said.
	   The man was visiting his son at a family friend's house. When he
saw the child, he pulled a meat cleaver and ax out from under his
clothing and attacked him.
	   The youngster managed to escape but his father chased him down a
street, caught him and hit him in the head with the ax before
fleeing.
