	   LONDON (AP) _ The U.S. dollar rose in European trading Tuesday
morning. Gold fell.
	   Dollar rates compared with late Monday:
	   _1.6748 German marks, up from 1.6738
	   _116.92 Japanese yen, up from 116.04
	   _1.3660 Swiss francs, up from 1.3616
