<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 12/22/1998 14:45:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w1970 &Cx1f; wstm-
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Iraq 6thLd-Writethru   12-22 0781
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Iraq, 6th Ld-Writethru,0793 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Iraq claims U.S.-British planes fired missiles at Basra
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITTING to CORRECT writethru sequence &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: New throughout to UPDATE with Iraq criticizing Kuwait, 3
children killed, protests by U.S. activists; CHANGES byline &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos BAG101, 103-104 &QL; 
 &UR; By LEON BARKHO &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
