<DATE_TIME> 12/22/1998 16:59:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w2121 &Cx1f; wstm-
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Lebanon-Israel 5thLd-Writethru   12-22 0500
