	   _ DAVIE, Florida _ Sports-Football-Dolphins-Playoffs. By Steven
Wine. Has moved.
 &UR; THE YEAR IN SPORTS:
	   NEW YORK _ Ten years ago, Florence Griffith Joyner dazzled the
world with her sensational sprint speed. This year, when Griffith
Joyner died suddenly, Marion Jones dazzled the world with her
sensational sprint speed.
	   Slug Sports-1998-Athletics. Expected by 0200 GMT.
